                      <div style="font-family:Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:24px;text-align:left;color:#dddddd;">
                        <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 46px; line-height: 60px; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Inknut Antiqua', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Představení platformy!</h1>
                      </div>
                    </td>
